name: Adobi's Real Open Mix [aah!]
description:
An alternative to ARealFlexibleMix with an opensource generative license*. Focusing on realism with room for creativity.

~ Adobi : opensource realism b/c saftle was having a winge

*v0.6 contains a merge reselling restriction removing from further releases

Focuses

  • Portraits, Landscapes

  • Realism, Paintings, Illustrations, CG, Concept Art

Settings

Sampling : Euler A (25), Heun, DDIM (60)
CFG Scale : 5.5 - 8.5
Hires. fix : R-ESRGAN 4x+, 25 Hires steps and Denoising strength 0.4

modelVersions.name: v0.6
modelVersions.description:
Warning : This version contains a reselling restriction from NED

Vae :
Recommended : vae-ft-mse-840000
Alternative : Anything VAE

Prime Models :

  • Liberty

  • Analog Diffusion

  • NeverEnding Dream < removing

  • Vintedois diffusion
